#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards/build_and_customize_dashboards.rst:163
msgid ""
"In the Dashboards app, go to :menuselection:`Configuration --> Dashboards`."
msgstr ""
"În aplicația Tablouri de bord, accesați :menuselection:`Configurare --> "
