#~ msgid ""
#~ "Enabling file centralization for a specific app automatically organizes "
#~ "all associated files into dedicated folders. To do so, go "
#~ "to :menuselection:`Documents --> Configuration --> Settings`. For "
#~ "example, enabling :guilabel:`Human Resources` makes HR documents "
#~ "automatically available in the :guilabel:`HR` folder, while documents "
#~ "related to Payroll are automatically available in the :guilabel:`Payroll` "
#~ "sub-folder. Select the desired folder from the dropdown list and select "
#~ "the :ref:`Tags <documents/tags>` to be added to the relevant files."
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "Activarea centralizării fișierelor pentru o anumită aplicație organizează "
#~ "automat toate fișierele asociate în foldere dedicate. Pentru a face acest "
#~ "lucru, mergi la :menuselection:`Documente --> Configurare --> Setări`. De "
#~ "exemplu, activarea :guilabel:`Resurse Umane` face ca documentele HR să "
